<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hab von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der sich gen der jüdischeit bey uns
                                <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> hat etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und als ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> meldt, sölt uns keinrley
                                <expan>ungnad<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> künig
                        und von dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> burggraf <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> entsteen, daz das
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> niht lieb <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, des
                                <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss
                        und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ein gut getrawn und
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch das umb ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. Aber als die sache
                                <expan>bish<ex>er</ex></expan> gehandelt ist, so hoffen wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des künigs und auch des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> ungnade niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dient</expan>
                        zu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> auch ir
                        ungnade <expan>ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schulden</expan> oder <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>.
                        Und wir <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> kurczlich
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
